:"Ahaha, we made sure to get you one. Here you go.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"2021birthdayStory-027-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"Nanami","body":"I really think you'll love it~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"2021birthdayStory-027-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"Rui","body":"I cannot imagine anyone enjoying something like this...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"2021birthdayStory-027-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"Toko","body":"You sound super confident, Nanami! I wonder what it could be~... Hey, what is this?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"2021birthdayStory-027-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":1,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsukushi","body":"It's a set of party goods! The shop Mashiro-chan told us about was selling them!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":29,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":29,"voiceId":"2021birthdayStory-027-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"Mashiro","body":"We were all talking about how you went to a sweets store for the first time the other day, so I thought maybe you'd never been to a discount store either.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"2021birthdayStory-027-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"Toko","body":"Ahaha, what's with this sash?! It says \"Birthday Girl!\"","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"2021birthdayStory-027-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"Toko","body":"And these sunglasses are a riot too! Rui, try these on for a sec!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"2021birthdayStory-027-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"Rui","body":"Why should I? You are the one who is celebrating their birthday.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"2021birthdayStory-027-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"Toko","body":"Aw, don't be so stingy! I mean, seriously, I'm the birthday girl today, so you should at least do this one little thing for me!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"2021birthdayStory-027-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"Rui","body":"I have no obligation to comply.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"2021birthdayStory-027-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"Toko","body":"Sigh~, you're such a drag~! Well, whatever! I'll try t